  "name": "transactionIntelligenceAgent",
  "description": "EliteTC Transaction Superagent \u2014 reads transaction data, deadlines, tasks, communications, and notifications, then executes actions: drafts addendums, composes emails, flags risks, summarizes status, and assists TCs and agents. Does NOT recalculate deadlines or override statuses.",
